displayName: Tabnine: AI Autocomplete & Chat for Javascript, Python, Typescript, PHP, Go, Java & more
shortDescription: AI coding assistant with AI code completions and AI code chat right in the IDE, helping developers by generating code, writing unit tests and documentation, explaining legacy code, and much more. Tabnine supports all major languages including JavaScript, Python, Java, Typescript c/c++ and more.
